entries.journal_entry_description: Somehow Stormtroopers have managed to survive within the walls of the research facility. Find them and get a situation report.
entries.task01_comm_message_text: [Han Solo] You should locate that Stormtrooper contingent Trig mentioned. If they are still alive they may be able to help point you in the right direction.
entries.task03_comm_message_text: [Han Solo] Dr. Cody and I were on the same prison ship. If it weren't for her, Chewie and me wouldn't be here.
entries.task04_journal_entry_description: Travel to the Imperial Research and Prison Facility and find the Stormtroopers Trig Longo mentioned.
entries.task05_comm_message_text: [Han Solo] What a mess. Looks like you found the facility. If you are lucky maybe the Stormtrooper contingent is still alive.
entries.task06_journal_entry_description: Search the interior of the facility for the Stormtroopers.
